WEBVTT

1
01:47.250 --> 01:50.500
<v Shaman>This blade has a dark past.</v>

2
01:51.800 --> 01:55.800
<v Shaman>It has shed much innocent blood.</v>

3
01:58.000 --> 02:01.450
<v Shaman>You're a fool for traveling alone,
so completely unprepared.</v>

4
02:01.750 --> 02:04.800
<v Shaman>You're lucky your blood's still flowing.</v>

5
02:05.250 --> 02:06.300
<v Sintel>Thank you.</v>

6
02:07.500 --> 02:09.000
<v Shaman>So...</v>

7
02:09.400 --> 02:13.800
<v Shaman>What brings you to
the land of the gatekeepers?</v>

8
02:15.000 --> 02:17.500
<v Sintel>I'm searching for someone.</v>

9
02:18.000 --> 02:22.200
<v Shaman>Someone very dear?
A kindred spirit?</v>

10
02:23.400 --> 02:25.000
<v Sintel>A dragon.</v>

11
02:28.850 --> 02:31.750
<v Shaman>A dangerous quest for a lone hunter.</v>

12
02:32.950 --> 02:35.870
<v Sintel>I've been alone for
as long as I can remember.</v>

13
03:27.250 --> 03:30.500
<v Sintel>We're almost done. Shhh...</v>

14
03:30.750 --> 03:33.500
<v Sintel>Hey, sit still.</v>

15
03:48.250 --> 03:52.250
<v Sintel>Good night, Scales.</v>

16
04:10.350 --> 04:13.850
<v Sintel>Get him, Scales! Come on!</v>

17
04:25.250 --> 04:28.250
<v Sintel>Scales?</v>

18
05:04.000 --> 05:07.500
<v Sintel>Yeah! Come on!</v>

19
05:38.750 --> 05:42.000
<v Sintel>Scales!</v>

20
07:25.850 --> 07:27.500
<v Sintel>I have failed.</v>

21
07:32.800 --> 07:36.500
<v Shaman>You've only failed to see...</v>

22
07:37.800 --> 07:40.500
<v Shaman>These are dragon lands, Sintel.</v>

23
07:40.850 --> 07:44.000
<v Shaman>You are closer than you know.</v>

24
09:17.600 --> 09:19.500
<v Sintel>Scales!</v>

25
10:21.600 --> 10:24.000
<v Sintel>Scales?</v>

26
10:26.200 --> 10:29.800
<v Sintel>Scales...</v>
